{
  "info": {
    "name": "Tech Challenge — Candido",
    "description": "API REST para gestão de ordens de serviço de oficina mecânica.\n\n**Como usar:**\n1. Execute `POST /api/v1/auth/login` — o token é salvo automaticamente na variável `{{token}}`\n2. Todas as demais requisições já usam `{{token}}` no Authorization header\n\n**Credenciais de demo:**\n- Recepcionista: recepcao@workshop.com / password\n- Mecânico: mecanico@workshop.com / password\n- Cliente: carlos@example.com / password",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — Recepcionista",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token salvo:', json.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"recepcao@workshop.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Mecânico",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"mecanico@workshop.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Cliente",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.token); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }, { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"carlos@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me — Usuário autenticado",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }, { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }, { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
